columns: Indicates if the variant is supported (Yes) or not supported (No) by RNA-Seq. If it has not been checked against RNA-Seq data, the value will be 'Unknown'.

A semicolon delimited list of supporting variant callers. If an asterisk is added to the caller name, this indicates the locus is a complex variant and this caller overlapped but did not support (e.g., not all callers can detect MNPs)
